## Key Files — Quick Reference

| File | Purpose | Load |
|------|---------|------|
| `.sfk/kernel/BOOTSTRAP.md` | Session entry point | Every session, first |
| `.sfk/kernel/RULES.md` | Sovereign governance — never override | Layer 0 |
| `.sfk/kernel/SOUL.md` | AI behavior contract | Layer 0 |
| `.sfk/kernel/project.toml` | Project identity, stack, URLs, env vars | Layer 0 |
| `.sfk/kernel/SYSTEM.md` | Technical and engineering standards | Layer 0 |
