| `memory/progress.md` | Current module state snapshot | On demand |
| `memory/logs/DEBUG-HISTORY.md` | Resolved bugs database (RAG source) | On bug tasks |
| `memory/logs/SESSION-AUDIT-CHECKLIST.md` | Pre-closure validation | Session close |

